# ML service: the trained model IS committed intentionally (see ml-service/README.md
# "Deploy" — Render serves the committed career_model.pkl instead of retraining on
# boot), so it must stay out of this file. Only its build artifacts are ignored.
ml-service/__pycache__/
ml-service/*.pyc
ml-service/.pytest_cache/
# Raw Stack Overflow survey download (~152 MB) — regenerate real_dataset_so.csv
# from it with preprocess_so.py; only the processed CSV is committed.
ml-service/data/

# Lock files (using bun.lock)
package-lock.json

# Claude Code / superpowers scratch state (task briefs, review diffs, progress ledger)
.superpowers/
*.tsbuildinfo

